    "summary": "Redux Toolkit and RTK Query: Practical Deep Notes Redux is predictable global state management. Redux Toolkit is the recommended way to write Redux logic. Store Typed hooks Slice Redux Toolkit uses Immer, so “mutating syntax” safely produces immutable updates....",
