    "title": "Redis, BullMQ, Queues, Kafka and Event-Driven Architecture: Full Expansion",
    "summary": "Redis, BullMQ, Queues, Kafka and Event-Driven Architecture: Full Expansion This JD directly mentions event-driven and async architectures. You must be able to explain why queues exist , what can fail, and how to design reliable processing. Why queues exist Wit...",
