    "title": "AWS Scaling Scenarios: Lambda, SQS, Glue and Event-Driven Pipelines",
    "summary": "AWS Scaling Scenarios: Lambda, SQS, Glue and Event-Driven Pipelines You have real AWS exposure, so this section helps you convert it into interview-ready architecture language. Lambda scaling mental model Lambda scales by running more concurrent function insta...",
