    "title": "Mini Project Route Map for This JD",
    "summary": "Mini Project Route Map for This JD Build one project that proves the exact JD skills: React frontend, Flask/FastAPI APIs, auth, PostgreSQL/MongoDB, Redis queue/cache, file upload, webhooks, async workers, search/sort/pagination, and deployment basics. Project ...",
