    "title": "C - Lambda Deep Dive",
    "summary": "PART C - Lambda Deep Dive 15. What is Lambda? ! Lambda Create Function screen data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAA1IAAAHHCAIAAAA6cP6JAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAERlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAA6ABAAMAAAABAAEAAKACAAQAAAABAAADUqADAAQAAAABAAABxwAA...",
