    "title": "I - Containers, EC2, ECS, EKS",
    "summary": "PART I - Containers, EC2, ECS, EKS 33. EC2 basics EC2 is virtual machine compute. Use EC2 when: - you need OS-level control - long-running process - custom runtime - background worker not suitable for Lambda - vendor software - legacy app EC2 production checkl...",
